{"tid":2086261,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【7.1上街】民主派多人毋懼惡法殺到接手發起遊行 籲港人堅持明上街","createTime":"2020-06-30T08:30:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-01T04:01:16.000Z","uid":25558,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"b72b878286248f12927019606c2d82639f5d2f5f","tid":2086261,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T08:30:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/local/20200630/4HPLAO723U6X3OZUZ7XVFTKJAI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200630%2F4HPLAO723U6X3OZUZ7XVFTKJAI%2F&d=r9GgQvVcrWtMp%2Fshn5VX%2Fz%2BdFj26OgxneTHruUJDv9o%3D&h=56c3aec3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200630%2F4HPLAO723U6X3OZUZ7XVFTKJAI%2F&h=79584957\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/local/20200630/4HPLAO723U6X3OZUZ7XVFTKJAI/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n【7.1上街】民主派多人毋懼惡法殺到接手發起遊行 籲港人堅持明上街<br />\n<br />\n有消息指港區國安法通過後會於7月1日凌晨起生效，而警方早前亦以武漢肺炎疫情及限聚令為由，向今年的7.1遊行發出反對通知書，屬17年來首次。雖然政權不斷打壓集會自由，但依然無阻港人發聲。民主派立法會議員胡志偉及區議員曾健成、陳榮泰、徐子見以及社民連陳皓桓等中午於終審法院外召開記者會，交代7.1安排。陳皓桓表示，將會以個人身份聯同另外四名議員發起7.1遊行，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">主題和時間會與民陣相同</span></span>，但<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>路線就會由改為由東角道行去遮打道。</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n陳皓桓、曾健成、胡志偉、陳榮泰、徐子見等五名民主派人士舉著「反對國安法，七一齊上街」標語見記者，其間高叫「七一街頭見」及「五大訴求，缺一不可」等口號。<br />\n<br />\n陳皓桓指，雖然今午6時會公佈民陣遊行上訴結果，但預料到當局必然不批准，所以決定提早於下午宣佈堅持發起遊行。遊行的主題和時間與民陣發起的一樣，為「反對國安惡法，堅持五大訴求」。遊行會於7.1下午2時舉行，但路線就會改為由東角道行去遮打道。陳皓桓表示，希望港人能不論膚色、種族及宗教，團結一致，<br />\n。。。。。。<br />\n持叫口號並用和平方式表達訴求，不會叫出席遊行人士不帶旗幟和不叫口號。<br />\n<br />\n東區區議員曾健成就指，於去年區議員選舉大勝的民主派是民意代表，所以他們責無旁貸，要構建平台讓市民抗惡法。他批評建制盲撐蘊藏無數魔鬼細節的惡法是出賣港人，又指一<br />\n。。。。。。<br />\n步一腳印地向當權者表達不滿。<br />\n<br />\n人大常委會今早全票通過港版國安法後，隨即傳出眾志「大地震」，又有主張港獨的組織解散。胡志偉回應事件時表示，就算有台前人物及政治組織在國安法下受打壓及取締<br />\n。。。。。。<br />\n是能和群眾走在一起，團結一致，對抗國安法的來臨。<br />\n<br />\n當記者問到胡志偉會否擔心議席受影響時，在旁的陳皓桓激動地表示：「七一唔上街，又談何選舉？七一唔上街又談何之後嘅自由同民主？又談何之後嘅抗爭？」他指現時應先將民主派初選及立法會選舉拋諸腦後，目前最重要的就是上街用人數告訴政府「唔好DQ任何人，唔好控告任何人，唔好打壓任何人嘅自由同民主。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n-----------------------------<br />\n蘋果25年系列ebook《讀果》上架：紀實現場 、世界前線 、逆權之路 、叱吒風雲 、守護真相<br />\n-----------------------------<br />\n<br />\n反送中一周年，《蘋果》整理大量涉及警察濫暴濫權等資料，製成詳盡資料庫，請按此閱讀圖表版本 ／純文字版本<br />\n-----------------------------<br />\n<br />\n打國際線 《蘋果》英文版免費試睇 按此了解更多<br />\n英文版已登錄新版《蘋果》App按此下載/更新<br />\n-----------------------------<br />\n<br />\nApp內1-Click訂閱《蘋果動新聞》<br />\n按此了解更多<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Wp2Kw1WiE1YMCmQF0IIfunUBx5o=/1440x810/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/VGWN6B2M62BXHNXIBXSTCECFVQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FWp2Kw1WiE1YMCmQF0IIfunUBx5o%3D%2F1440x810%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FVGWN6B2M62BXHNXIBXSTCECFVQ.jpg&h=2c548074&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n(左一起)區議員曾健成、社民連陳皓桓、議員胡志偉、區議員徐子見、區議員陳榮泰。本報記者攝。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/TSYibIPbon_itcr8A-tjTQRmPU8=/2449x1632/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/FBQLII356B4X35UD5GFIC333KY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FTSYibIPbon_itcr8A-tjTQRmPU8%3D%2F2449x1632%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FFBQLII356B4X35UD5GFIC333KY.jpg&h=c2dcc2f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n(左一起)區議員曾健成、社民連陳皓桓、議員胡志偉、區議員徐子見、區議員陳榮泰。本報記者攝。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/K5229fb_SJZenEMxx9-tj0we0dk=/2449x1633/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/64NPBTHRVTCP6NU3D6HSBNCHUI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FK5229fb_SJZenEMxx9-tj0we0dk%3D%2F2449x1633%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F64NPBTHRVTCP6NU3D6HSBNCHUI.jpg&h=53f8faa0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n陳皓桓(左2)聯同胡志偉(右1)等人發起遊行。本報記者攝。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/FiWDl8bXkVsUu3AY8TBqS_Fvb5I=/640x426/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/WNYRC2SEPN5HU2AX6GCXAIWY5M.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FFiWDl8bXkVsUu3AY8TBqS_Fvb5I%3D%2F640x426%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FWNYRC2SEPN5HU2AX6GCXAIWY5M.jpg&h=cf74442e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n樂康區區議員曾健成指，港人明天應一步一腳印地向當權者表達不滿。本報記者攝。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/ff5-uhwd5VXZwDt5hAt94ZSc7sU=/640x426/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/QYR63YHUKKVNUJD7HH4RWSWAY4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fff5-uhwd5VXZwDt5hAt94ZSc7sU%3D%2F640x426%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FQYR63YHUKKVNUJD7HH4RWSWAY4.jpg&h=b09a0c10&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n小西灣區區議員陳榮泰指，明天的7.1遊行是一項指標。本報記者攝。"},{"pid":"dbafe5ae271b658c0c42a48eaa24268c953fa9d4","tid":2086261,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T08:33:30.000Z","msg":"聽日見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"543a306cf52e54da014dae45b5039ecd00686aed","tid":2086261,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T08:40:51.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"7f01831458ed09624611a33ac71835bdeb4a8a4d","tid":2086261,"uid":271807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T08:43:25.000Z","msg":"肅然起勁"},{"pid":"b89aef6a0d7f209d2079ea7ca51737c4f8201f75","tid":2086261,"uid":35924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"re